trans-unit.source: Compares two objects for equivalence, where string comparisons are case-sensitive.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner to objekter for likhet, der det skilles strengsammenligninger.

trans-unit.source: This class is the default implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er standard implementering av den <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.IComparer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> class is the implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.IComparer> interface that performs case-insensitive string comparisons.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>klassen er implementeringen av den <xref:System.Collections.IComparer>grensesnitt som utfører samlingstype strengsammenligninger.</xref:System.Collections.IComparer> </xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>

trans-unit.source: Comparison procedures use the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName> of the current thread unless otherwise specified.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning prosedyrer bruk av <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>for gjeldende tråd hvis ikke annet er angitt.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentCulture%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: String comparisons might have different results depending on the culture.
trans-unit.target: Strengsammenligninger kan ha forskjellige resultater, alt etter kulturen.

trans-unit.source: For more information on culture-specific comparisons, see the <xref:System.Globalization> namespace and [Globalization and Localization](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om kultur-spesifikke sammenligninger, kan du se den <xref:System.Globalization>navneområde og [globalisering og lokalisering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Globalization>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Collections.Comparer"></xref> class using the specified <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Collections.Comparer"> </xref> klasse parametersettet med de angitte <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName>.

trans-unit.source: Comparison procedures use the specified <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo?displayProperty=fullName> to determine the sort order and casing rules.

trans-unit.source: Performs a case-sensitive comparison of two objects of the same type and returns a value indicating whether one is less than, equal to, or greater than the other.
trans-unit.target: Utfører en skiller sammenligning av to objekter av samme type, og returnerer en verdi som angir om en er mindre enn, lik eller større enn den andre.

trans-unit.source: If `a` implements <xref:System.IComparable>, then `a`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `a` implementerer <xref:System.IComparable>, deretter `a`.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: `CompareTo` (`b`) is returned; otherwise, if `b` implements <xref:System.IComparable>, then the negated result of `b`.
trans-unit.target: `CompareTo`(`b`) returneres; ellers, hvis `b` implementerer <xref:System.IComparable>, deretter negative resultatet av `b`.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: `CompareTo` (`a`) is returned.
trans-unit.target: `CompareTo`(`a`) returneres.

trans-unit.source: Comparing `null` with any type is allowed and does not generate an exception when using <xref:System.IComparable>.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligning av `null` med et hvilket som er tillatt, og ikke generere et unntak ved <xref:System.IComparable>.</xref:System.IComparable>

trans-unit.source: When sorting, `null` is considered to be less than any other object.
trans-unit.target: Når du sorterer, `null` anses å være mindre enn andre objekter.
